      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what? i dont get the goblin thing. can you just give me the actual math? like if i have a $30,000 loan at 5% interest and i pay $300 a month, can you show me how much of that is actually hitting the principal vs the interest in the first few months? i just need the numbers.",
